{"tid":1645832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果眾籌 黑狗爆料有錢收點睇？","createTime":"2019-10-11T04:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T19:35:32.000Z","uid":122059,"like":20,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"aed3191b7cdb446ea94deb6127d0a0aa57371595","tid":1645832,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"我相信好多黑狗都有好多不可公開既資料係手上<br />\n佢地到宜家越黎越難翻身 所以無論咩事都會去到最盡<br />\n再者 班狗 毅進畢業 佢地辭職再搵唔返咁高人工既工<br />\n為左錢 同驚比人清算 唯有老撚都要撐落去<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個時候 諗下 比d好處一班想脫離全港最大黑社會既黑狗<br />\n向佢地伸出橄欖枝<br />\n如果呢班死垃圾 可以拎到d 可靠既資料 文件 或者 事件 投靠返香港人呢邊 唔做CCP 走狗<br />\n我地提供一個tg 比佢地爆料 向佢地保證 有錢收 保密<br />\n如果佢地提供既資料 得到證實  可以考慮係清算名單剔除佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbda3e7b760927ac1a0a41857ecc10491d1dcba9","tid":1645832,"uid":325449,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"算吧啦，有良心就會出聲，課金既都唔係良心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229bcb793caa2a59fbe2f6dea3d267a42b4b1a2a","tid":1645832,"uid":122059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbda3e7b760927ac1a0a41857ecc10491d1dcba9","tid":1645832,"uid":325449,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"算吧啦，有良心就會出聲，課金既都唔係良心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"佢地係驚比人清算"},{"pid":"d90932619c63aff4e932a84a2e1ae6a5aff3e01e","tid":1645832,"uid":122059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:54:32.000Z","msg":"對於佢地黎講出賣狗隊 根本無著數<br />\n無著數既野 邊有人做？<br />\n如果仲係保持 算吧啦 佢地係有良心早就出左黎呢個心態<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係錯撚曬</span></span><br />\n你想佢轉白 都要比d 動力佢地 唔係就咁一句<br />\n實際少少諗 其實班死垃圾 因為無得揀<br />\n但如果你比選擇佢 話唔定係可以令到一部分垃圾 做返一個人"},{"pid":"3fc8b2d4faaec6556dbce957f4494c423cdeb15a","tid":1645832,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:55:13.000Z","msg":"呢個眾籌搵唔到多錢，要公眾人士掉大舊錢先有吸引力"},{"pid":"733fed98407426a9b189363ee92f040e8749575e","tid":1645832,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc8b2d4faaec6556dbce957f4494c423cdeb15a","tid":1645832,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:55:13.000Z","msg":"呢個眾籌搵唔到多錢，要公眾人士掉大舊錢先有吸引力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:58:29.000Z","msg":"班垃圾最驚除左起底 係佢地會比人清算<br />\n如果可以比一個選擇佢地 爆d勁料<br />\n唔單止唔會清算 仲可以有錢收<br />\n分分鐘拎埋光環<br />\n其實係可以吸引到呢班想爆料 但係覺得無著數既垃圾 出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d2910bad84c7dcda0976e00ce8d3d9d11e3b4b","tid":1645832,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edcabfab0e59b8b9ac6d877ba227678fa2bfe4a8","tid":1645832,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd611090c5d9b33071cab85ba36128c9e79ff0db","tid":1645832,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a50e449761baaf2665ed3cb9ec4945ecd11171cd","tid":1645832,"uid":29551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:05:47.000Z","msg":"有無諗過收錢企出嚟會俾人告老妨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攞返嚟嘅證據都未必上到庭，揾隻狗放流料就收你皮"},{"pid":"8ac48ef38adb49975107016220956df52dd578c7","tid":1645832,"uid":177219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"重賞之下必有勇夫"},{"pid":"a8d6dc487a8cbbefa3170cd8ee4fec89c821a5fe","tid":1645832,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a50e449761baaf2665ed3cb9ec4945ecd11171cd","tid":1645832,"uid":29551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:05:47.000Z","msg":"有無諗過收錢企出嚟會俾人告老妨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攞返嚟嘅證據都未必上到庭，揾隻狗放流料就收你皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:12:1